Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight, multiplatform Modbus library.
 Liblightmodbus is aimed to run on personal computers
 as well as on smaller systems, like AVR micro-controllers.
 Library requires minimal resources to run.
